reviewText: This DVD is really funny. It's soo good to see and hear these comics before their careers took off they are all so funny from the beginning up to now.
I remember watching this show when I was younger :)  and continue to see the comedians today and seeing this now is just as funny as I remember,
Very very very funny. Recommend it if you want to laugh. It is defiantly a great price so highly recommend it.

The DVD is good with the exception of the Jamie Foxx piece, it is also on the bonus disk that i already have. The Seller "Empire Palm Videos" was very prompt to fill my order and i was very happy with their service.

I bought this DVD under the impression that it was 300 minutes. It is only 60 minutes, just 2 episodes. What a rip-off! It also said that Mike Epps was on it and he was not. I am VERY disappointed in the false advertising of this product.

This video had me ROLLIN!!! Hosted by Martin Lawrence: AdeleGivens (Do I look like a ...... Lady OUR WHAT!! She's Crazy! Some of the stuff that comes out of this Lady's mouth had me on the floor! She talks about how You don't need a man! All you need is your Gynocologist! Then D.L Hughley was too funny! This Video is 55min of non stop laughter! hosted by Martin Lawrence.
Not as funny as I thought
I am happy with my purchase.

Not a bad selection, however, I wish there was more!!!  overall I liked the video

Thanks Again for a smooth delivery!!
Excellent line up of fun filled laughter. Jamie Foxx is Hilarious. You all are going to love it so much.
